headline: 2 Reasons to Avoid NXPI and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: NXP Semiconductors has been treading water for the past six months, recording a small return of 4% while holding steady at $237.49. The stock also fell short of the S&P 500’s 10% gain during that period.
